#| "symlink will point to the file/directory you right-clicked on. If the "
#| "file you right-clicked on is a symlink, you will also be presented with "
#| "the <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Link Handling</guisubmenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Redirect Link</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option that will "
